summary_to_eng: Can't login to LMS staging Vietnam
Text_Summa: Can't login to LMS staging Vietnam We found that the problem was that SSO was saving users to one database (jackfruitstaging) but lms was accessing another (jfstating) using different username and password as well (user: jackfruitstaging; password: jackfruitstaging@edumall - that's what sso was using) and (user: jfstaging; password: jfstaging@edumall - that's what lms was using). After login SSO was redirecting users to LMS where in callback LMS tried to retrieve a user from the database by ID which's stored in cookies but it was always null and LMS was redirecting to SSO which was correctly finding a user from database by id of cookies and was redirecting back to LMS. This operation was performing recursively. We changed the database of LMS to the old one which SSO refers to. And it works
